title: A bit of Braumix inspired Braum jungling

embed.description: Hi everyone, got inspired by the LoL Braumix so I decided to play meta jungle Braum, and he's op as hell. If you like the video, please like, subscribe and share. I run this channel as a hobby and love coming home from work and doing this stuff each night.

body: If anyone wants a 'how to' for jungling Braum, help get those likes up and I'll do a commentary for ya'll.  Cheers.

replies.body:
Fantastic, now I have not only another AP tank jungle that I can build as an on hit fighter if required, but also another reason to play Braum.

Thanks for sharing!
